Generates IR:

	FOR C:

	clang -S -emit-llvm

	FOR FORTRAN:

	You need to create the dynamic lib dragonegg.so:
		Look at libs/dragonegg-3.3.src/README

	-S -fplugin=/path/to/dragonegg.so -fplugin-arg-dragonegg-emit-ir

Extract loops:

	opt -S -loop-extract your_file.s -o output_file

Instrument loops:

	opt -S -load /src/llvm-3.3.src/Release+Asserts/lib/LLVMLoop-instrumentation.so -loop-instrumentation your_file.s -o output_file
